	One H3VP entry:
		tag:             10 bits
		hist0+hist1+hist2: 192 bits
		diff:            64 bits
		instance ctr:    7 bits
		num_ret:         2 bits
		conf per pred (x3): 7 bits each
		failed flags:    3 bits
		bits/H3VP entry: 299 bits
	Total storage cost = 1024 entries x 299 bits = 306176 bits
